# Convert Certification and Key files for APNS to be used with apns.php
#
# 1. copy the provided certification and key file to
#	apns-dev-cert.p12
#	apns-dev-key.p12
#
# 2. run make
#	using the passwords given
#	when converting the key file, enter a new password
#
# 3. copy the device token publihed by the IOS App to in MQTT
#	 under "mqttitude/<user>/<device>/deviceToken" into apns.php
#
#    or do this to PyAPNS/jp.py
#
# 4. run php -f apns.php
#
#    or cd PyAPNS and run python jp.py
#

